{"id":14266,"date":"2025-11-17T11:30:16","date_gmt":"2025-11-17T16:30:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?p=14266"},"modified":"2025-11-17T11:23:27","modified_gmt":"2025-11-17T16:23:27","slug":"une-etudiante-en-sciences-de-la-nature-recipiendaire-de-la-bourse-sram-international","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/une-etudiante-en-sciences-de-la-nature-recipiendaire-de-la-bourse-sram-international\/","title":{"rendered":"Une \u00e9tudiante en Sciences de la nature r\u00e9cipiendaire de la bourse SRAM International"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"chapeau\">La <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/a-propos\/cegep-citoyen\/fondation\/\">Fondation du c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent<\/a> a eu le plaisir de remettre cet automne une bourse de 500 $ au nom du <a href=\"http:\/\/sram.qc.ca\/fr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Service r\u00e9gional d&rsquo;admission du Montr\u00e9al m\u00e9tropolitain<\/a> (SRAM) destin\u00e9e \u00e0 la communaut\u00e9 \u00e9tudiante issue de l&rsquo;international.<\/p>\n<p>Cette bourse est attribu\u00e9e par tirage \u00e0 chaque session parmi toutes les personnes admises au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent \u00e0 la session d\u2019automne, provenant de l&rsquo;international et dont la demande d\u2019admission a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9pos\u00e9e aupr\u00e8s du SRAM.<\/p>\n<p>F\u00e9licitations \u00e0 Sara Otmani, \u00e9tudiante en <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/programmes\/sciences-de-la-nature\/\">Sciences de la nature<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Nous tenons \u00e0 remercier chaleureusement celles et ceux qui ont contribu\u00e9 \u00e0 rendre cette initiative possible, notamment nos g\u00e9n\u00e9reux donateurs et donatrices.<\/p>\n<div style=\"background: #ECF2F8; padding: 10px;\">\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Le saviez-vous ?<\/h3>\n<p>La Fondation du C\u00e9gep offre diff\u00e9rentes bourses tout au long de l\u2019ann\u00e9e aux personnes \u00e9tudiantes du c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/a-propos\/cegep-citoyen\/fondation\/\">D\u00e9couvrez en plus sur la Fondation<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>La Fondation du c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent a eu le plaisir de remettre cet automne une bourse de 500 $ au nom du Service r\u00e9gional d&rsquo;admission du Montr\u00e9al m\u00e9tropolitain (SRAM) destin\u00e9e \u00e0 la communaut\u00e9 \u00e9tudiante issue de l&rsquo;international. Cette bourse est attribu\u00e9e par tirage \u00e0 chaque session parmi toutes les personnes admises au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":14283,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[199],"etiquette-interne":[2305,2313,2357],"class_list":["post-14266","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-fondation","etiquette-interne-institutionnel","etiquette-interne-fondation","etiquette-interne-milieu-de-vie"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-04 22:11:50","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14266","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14266"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14266\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":14282,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14266\/revisions\/14282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14283"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14266"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14266"},{"taxonomy":"sujet-actualite","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/sujet-actualite?post=14266"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=14266"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}